Package cycronix.ctlib

Java interface to CloudTurbine read/write utilities

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ArgHandler
    Utility class for building and parsing commmand line arguments.
    CTdata
    CloudTurbine utility class to manage ArrayList of time,data couples
    CTftp
    CloudTurbine utility class that extends CTwriter class to write via FTP versus local filesystem
    CTmap
    A CloudTurbine utility class to manage TreeMap of name-CTdata pairs
    CTreader
    A class to read data from CloudTurbine folder/files.
    CTtrim
    A class to trim (ring-buffer loop) CloudTurbine folder/files.
    CTwriter
    A class to write data to CloudTurbine folder/files.
